PropertyDescription.Name: AlarmConditionState
PropertyDescription.Value: if $'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.AlmActH' || $'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.AlmActHH' then $'pr::HourCounter:Alarm Global Properties:AlarmConditionState_Descendants' else 0

PropertyDescription.Name: AlarmPriorityLevel
PropertyDescription.Value: if $'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.AlmActH' || $'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.AlmActHH' then $'pr::HourCounter:Alarm Global Properties:AlarmPriorityLevel_Descendants' else 0

PropertyDescription.Name: OverrideValue
PropertyDescription.Value: String($'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.Hours') + " h " + String($'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.Minutes') + " m"

PropertyDescription.Name: OverrideValue
PropertyDescription.Value: String($'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.DailyHours') + " h " + String($'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.DailyMinutes') + " m"

PropertyDescription.Name: Value
PropertyDescription.Value: if $'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_ManSel' then Variant(False) else Variant(True)

PropertyDescription.Name: AlarmConditionState
PropertyDescription.Value: if $'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.AlmActH' && !$'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.AlmActHH' then $'pr::HourCounter:Alarm Global Properties:AlarmConditionState_Descendants' else 0

PropertyDescription.Name: AlarmPriorityLevel
PropertyDescription.Value: if $'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.AlmActH' && !$'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:LIO.Out.AlmActHH' then $'pr::HourCounter:Alarm Global Properties:AlarmPriorityLevel_Descendants' else 0

PropertyDescription.Name: Maximum
PropertyDescription.Value: if $'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_LimHH' > 0 then Variant($'pr::HourCounter:Control Module:FPIntPar.FP_LimHH') else Empty
